      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_002414_000269_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
            <p>Col. Charles Pettit</p>
            <p>corner Walnut &amp;front St.</p>
            <pb n="2" facs="0012_002414_000269_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e45"/>
            <p>Col. Charles Pettit</p>
            <p>Sir</p>
            <p>Mrs. Copeland the Administrar. to Asa Copelands Estate, Has requested me to propare a Reference for the Settlement of her
				       Accts. with The Insurance company of North America on your appointing a Referee and mentioning a time &amp;place of
				       meeting  She will be ready on her part.</p>
            <p>She Judges this the most proper mode of Settlement to justify her as Adminir,</p>
            <p>Shall be obliged by your reply And am Respectfully</p>
            <p>Sir</p>
            <p>Your Obdt Servt._</p>
            <p>Peter W. Gallandet</p>
            <p>20 Decr 1799</p>
            <pb n="3" facs="0012_002414_000269_0003.jpg" xml:id="d4e65"/>
            <p>20th  Dec  1799</p>
            <p>
               <unclear reason="illegible" resp="pw">Thosrm</unclear>Ewing</p>
            <p>respecting Case of Asa</p>
            <p>Copeland  &amp;Sloop Maria</p>
            <p>See Jon  <unclear reason="illegible" resp="pw">Donnth</unclear>&amp;Co</p>
         </div>
      </body>
